Application::BackupAndRestore
=============================

Backup and Restore your Files and Folders incrementally.

APPLICATION NAME

	BackupAndRestore

INSTALLATION

To install this module open a terminal window, cd into the directory and
type the following:

	perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   sudo make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires

	tar
	file-roller

A Locale of en_GB.utf8 is needed and probably installed

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS

Linux or äquivalent Unix System. Tested under Ubuntu (Hardy Heron)

